data.description: PRICE ADJUSTMENT!!  A wonderful 4 bedroom, 3 full bath triple split plan in the fabulous Panther Trace Community is now available!! Room for the whole family in this well maintained home . GORGEOUS updated kitchen is the heart of this spacious house, with miles of countertops, tons of storage, 2 closet pantry's, breakfast dinette, and huge breakfast bar to feed a crowd! Luxurious primary suite includes a lovely bath with tons of storage, walk in closet and a separate shower and soaking tub. Formal spaces adorned with crown moulding. There is also a dedicated study/office for working @ home. 3 car garage is a bonus allowing for plenty of storage. The screened lanai is a perfect place to wind down at the end of the day.  Enjoy the fenced backyard with plenty of room for kids, pets and a pool! ! Home is located very close to the Community pool, clubhouse, tennis courts, volleyball pit, pickle ball! Roof is only 2 years old! Solar panels keep the electric costs to a minimum. This is the PERFECT active family home, with room for everyone!
